<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 16:07:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>民主党高层不会就即将向以色列出售 F-15 给予拜登橡皮图章，这可能会改变游戏规则</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/potential-game-changer-top-democrat-wont-give-biden-rubber-stamp-on-f-15-sales-to-israel/0000018e-c36d-d1b7-a3af-e76f98460000</link><description>美国外交事务委员会众议员格雷戈里·米克斯宣布，他正在等待拜登就以色列在加沙的行为做出保证，然后才会批准向以色列出售价值 180 亿美元的 F-15 战斗机。米克斯说：“我认为无差别轰炸已经够了。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 15:55:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/potential-game-changer-top-democrat-wont-give-biden-rubber-stamp-on-f-15-sales-to-israel/0000018e-c36d-d1b7-a3af-e76f98460000</guid></item><item><title>“证据不足”：德国在国际法院否认协助以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/flimsy-evidence-germany-denies-charge-of-aiding-alleged-israeli-genocide-in-gaza-at-icj/0000018e-c328-d6f4-afaf-ef6aa3890000</link><description>德国的一名法律顾问表示，尼加拉瓜在联合国最高法院的案件很仓促，应该被驳回，因为德国和其他西方国家面临着向以色列出口武器的抗议。德国是以色列最大的武器供应国之一</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/flimsy-evidence-germany-denies-charge-of-aiding-alleged-israeli-genocide-in-gaza-at-icj/0000018e-c328-d6f4-afaf-ef6aa3890000</guid></item><item><title>由于极右翼部长的压力，以色列安全内阁将讨论人质交易进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/security-cabinet-set-to-discuss-gaza-truce-progress-due-to-far-right-ministers-pressure/0000018e-c31f-d480-a99e-cf5ff2030000</link><description>有报道称，以色列国防军已从加沙大部分地区撤出，停火和人质协议也取得了进展，极右翼部长本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇展示了他们的联盟力量，要求参与有关以色列未来的决策过程。战争</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:33:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/security-cabinet-set-to-discuss-gaza-truce-progress-due-to-far-right-ministers-pressure/0000018e-c31f-d480-a99e-cf5ff2030000</guid></item><item><title>德国公司以加沙战争为由拒绝向以色列残奥会提供门球供应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/german-firm-refuses-to-provide-goalball-supply-to-israeli-paralympics-citing-gaza-war/0000018e-c2ec-d6f4-afaf-eeeec0b20000</link><description>德国公司 KSG GmbH 做出这一决定是因为它相信“采取这一立场对于坚持我们的原则和支持和平解决冲突的努力是必要的”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:20:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/german-firm-refuses-to-provide-goalball-supply-to-israeli-paralympics-citing-gaza-war/0000018e-c2ec-d6f4-afaf-eeeec0b20000</guid></item><item><title>高级官员表示，本-格维尔的警察局长任命将完成他对以色列警察的接管</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-will-complete-his-takeover-of-the-police-top-officials-say/0000018e-c295-dc93-adce-eef5af430000</link><description>“罪犯第一次任命专员”：以色列警方高层将本-格维尔对警察局长的选择描述为极右翼国家安全部长及其幕僚长（前山顶人物）的“傀儡”和“唯唯诺诺的人”青年活动家</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:10:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-will-complete-his-takeover-of-the-police-top-officials-say/0000018e-c295-dc93-adce-eef5af430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长决定独立日仪式在没有观众的情况下举行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-decides-independence-day-ceremony-to-be-held-without-an-audience/0000018e-c2c1-d480-a99e-ced72cc20000</link><description>在决定仪式不包括烟花表演后，利库德集团部长米里·雷格夫现在表示，出于安全考虑，仪式将在没有观众的情况下举行，并提前拍摄。在 Ynet 新闻播出的一段录音中，在加沙被扣押的人质的母亲要求雷格夫取消仪式</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:47:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-decides-independence-day-ceremony-to-be-held-without-an-audience/0000018e-c2c1-d480-a99e-ced72cc20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列市长因伊朗袭击紧急准备而引起居民恐慌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/mayor-of-israeli-city-panics-residents-over-emergency-preparations-for-iranian-attack/0000018e-c28c-d877-a7be-f2ff6e170000</link><description>以色列南部城市阿什杜德上周在以色列杀害一名伊朗高级将军后发表声明，呼吁该市每户家庭“组织起来，做好应对与广泛导弹有关的紧急情况的准备”攻击&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:37:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/mayor-of-israeli-city-panics-residents-over-emergency-preparations-for-iranian-attack/0000018e-c28c-d877-a7be-f2ff6e170000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府正在用资金消除绿线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-government-is-eliminating-the-green-line-with-money/0000018e-bcd4-d7ee-a39e-fdfebb870000</link><description>预算逐个预算，法律逐个法律：从强迫手机公司扩大在被占领土的覆盖范围到促进公共资金向定居点转移的法律。这就是内塔尼亚胡的极右政府正在努力实现事实上的吞并</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:06:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-government-is-eliminating-the-green-line-with-money/0000018e-bcd4-d7ee-a39e-fdfebb870000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其和以色列贸易针锋相对，关系进一步恶化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-09/ty-article/turkey-slams-israel-with-export-sanctions-until-gaza-cease-fire-achieved/0000018e-c25b-d6f4-afaf-ee5b08c00000</link><description>土耳其已经停止向以色列发送任何可用于军事目的的货物。以色列表示将通过限制从土耳其进口的产品来回应这些措施</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:11:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-09/ty-article/turkey-slams-israel-with-export-sanctions-until-gaza-cease-fire-achieved/0000018e-c25b-d6f4-afaf-ee5b08c00000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯赢了吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/has-hamas-won/0000018e-c21d-d1b7-a3af-e71f0f590000</link><description>哈马斯颠覆了以色列在军事上所向披靡的剧本，暴露了其国际支持的脆弱性，引发了对其长期可持续性的严峻质疑。西方、温和的阿拉伯国家、以色列和巴勒斯坦权力机构有责任阻止他们取得任何最终胜利</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:40:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/has-hamas-won/0000018e-c21d-d1b7-a3af-e71f0f590000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府报告显示，自 10 月 7 日和加沙战争以来，以色列收到的捐款已达 14 亿美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/donations-to-israel-since-oct-7-and-gaza-war-top-1-4-billion-israeli-govt-report-finds/0000018e-c219-d480-a99e-ce5f096c0000</link><description>新报告显示，这 14 亿美元中约有一半是由北美犹太联合会及其 146 个成员组织筹集的，大约 58,000 名志愿者从国外飞往以色列</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:41:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/donations-to-israel-since-oct-7-and-gaza-war-top-1-4-billion-israeli-govt-report-finds/0000018e-c219-d480-a99e-ce5f096c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长因法律困难否决本格维尔的警察发言人候选人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-vetoes-appointment-of-ben-gvirs-candidate-as-police-spokesperson/0000018e-c1b2-d6f4-afaf-edf2c6ca0000</link><description>消息人士称，如果国家安全部长批准提拔本-格维尔在警察内部的同僚，以色列警察局长同意聘请本-格维尔的候选人担任警察发言人</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 08:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-vetoes-appointment-of-ben-gvirs-candidate-as-police-spokesperson/0000018e-c1b2-d6f4-afaf-edf2c6ca0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事演习缓解加沙压力，为人质谈判提供关键时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-maneuvers-ease-pressure-on-gaza-presenting-key-moment-for-hostage-talks/0000018e-bf36-d92b-adaf-ff763abc0000</link><description>以色列国防军从加沙南部撤军以及援助物资数量增加两倍可能有助于谈判，或者让辛瓦尔觉得不必着急，从而威胁到以色列脆弱的联盟。与此同时，哈马斯和巴勒斯坦权力机构为控制加沙剩余的民事机构进行了一场悄悄的战争</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-maneuvers-ease-pressure-on-gaza-presenting-key-moment-for-hostage-talks/0000018e-bf36-d92b-adaf-ff763abc0000</guid></item><item><title>报告：美国以色列-哈马斯停战提议包括让15万巴勒斯坦人返回加沙北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-live/naval-iron-dome-intercepts-target-over-red-sea-for-first-time-hamas-no-progress-on-talks/0000018e-c0a2-db65-a7af-d0aab8ef0000</link><description>纽约时报：伊朗在中东经营秘密走私路线，向约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人运送武器 ■ 法国、埃及、约旦领导人呼吁加沙“立即停火” ■ 哈马斯称以色列的提议未能满足巴勒斯坦人的要求，将继续回顾一下 ■ 内塔尼亚胡称拉法行动日期已定</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 02:27:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-live/naval-iron-dome-intercepts-target-over-red-sea-for-first-time-hamas-no-progress-on-talks/0000018e-c0a2-db65-a7af-d0aab8ef0000</guid></item><item><title>费城剧院因担心亲巴勒斯坦人的强烈反对而取消放映以色列电影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/philadelphia-theater-nixes-screening-of-israeli-film-over-fear-of-pro-palestinian-backlash/0000018e-bfdc-db65-a7af-ffdcb9a70000</link><description>布林莫尔电影学院原定在费城举行的年度以色列电影节上放映一部关于以色列音乐家耶胡达·波利克 (Yehuda Poliker) 的纪录片，但在提前一天通知后就取消了该学院</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 22:54:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/philadelphia-theater-nixes-screening-of-israeli-film-over-fear-of-pro-palestinian-backlash/0000018e-bfdc-db65-a7af-ffdcb9a70000</guid></item><item><title>参议员伊丽莎白·沃伦：以色列在加沙的行动可能在法律上构成种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/sen-elizabeth-warren-israels-actions-in-gaza-may-legally-constitute-genocide/0000018e-bf87-d6f4-afaf-bfc7919d0000</link><description>尽管几名批评以色列的进步派众议院议员表示，他们个人认为这次军事行动构成了种族灭绝，但没有人敢直截了当地这么说。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 21:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/sen-elizabeth-warren-israels-actions-in-gaza-may-legally-constitute-genocide/0000018e-bf87-d6f4-afaf-bfc7919d0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔：最新提案将弥合人质谈判中的分歧；哈马斯否认进展报告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/qatar-latest-proposal-bridges-gaps-in-hostage-talks-hamas-denies-reports-of-progress/0000018e-bf65-d480-a99e-ff77153b0000</link><description>调解员等待以色列和哈马斯的回应；以色列消息人士称，协议要求哈马斯提供第一阶段释放的40名人质的姓名，并保证他们还活着，以换取原则上同意允许巴勒斯坦人返回加沙北部的家园</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 20:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/qatar-latest-proposal-bridges-gaps-in-hostage-talks-hamas-denies-reports-of-progress/0000018e-bf65-d480-a99e-ff77153b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡审判的关键证人拿执法部门开玩笑。现在他正在付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/key-witness-in-netanyahu-trial-made-a-joke-of-law-enforcement-now-hes-paying-the-price/0000018e-bf19-d6f4-afaf-bf5b478e0000</link><description>什洛莫·菲尔伯在代表国家作证之前就明确表明了他的忠诚所在。在检察官宣布计划取消与他的协议后，下一步就是对他提出指控</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 20:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/key-witness-in-netanyahu-trial-made-a-joke-of-law-enforcement-now-hes-paying-the-price/0000018e-bf19-d6f4-afaf-bf5b478e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列迷失了方向，内塔尼亚胡不知道他要把我们带到哪里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-is-lost-and-netanyahu-has-no-idea-where-hes-taking-us/0000018e-be71-d480-a99e-fe77a9cf0000</link><description>当我的导航应用程序被以色列军队的 GPS 干扰器弄得毫无用处时，我突然意识到，我在路上感受到的不安全和不确定感与 10 月 7 日以来的全国情绪完全一致</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 18:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-is-lost-and-netanyahu-has-no-idea-where-hes-taking-us/0000018e-be71-d480-a99e-fe77a9cf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家检察官表示将撤销在内塔尼亚胡审判中与关键证人达成的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-attorney-says-it-will-revoke-agreement-with-key-witness-in-netanyahu-trial/0000018e-becd-d480-a99e-fedfb5c00000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的心腹、政府 4000 号案件的关键证人什洛莫·菲尔伯 (Shlomo Filber) 在出庭作证时未能遵守协议条款。在作证期间，菲尔伯撤回了他之前提出的几项主张，导致检察官要求法庭宣布他为敌对证人</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 18:07:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-attorney-says-it-will-revoke-agreement-with-key-witness-in-netanyahu-trial/0000018e-becd-d480-a99e-fedfb5c00000</guid></item></channel></rss>